(4019, 850, 'Ipswich Dark Ale', 3, 38, '6', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Rich in color and bold in taste, our U.S. style Brown Ale combines roasted malt with two additions of specialty selected hops to produce a well-balanced ale with a satisfying finish.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
