(4184, 1072, 'Mocha Porter / New Porter', 2, 25, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Dedicated to the chocolate lover in each of us. Mocha Porter was once known as New Porter, in honor of the town of Newport, Oregon and home of Rogue Ales. The January/February 1995 issue of Mens Health magazine features a bottle of Rogue New Porter (today', 0, '2010-07-22'),
