(4199, 1072, 'Issaquah Bullfrog Ale', 11, 116, '0', '0', '0', 0, '', 'An American style wheat beer and an Issaquah Brewhouse origina. Light in color and body and served with a lemon, Bullfrog is crisp, refreshing and goes down easy. Take a flying leap! Bullfrog Ale took the Silver Medal at the 2004 Great American Beer Fest', 0, '2010-07-22'),
