(4210, 1072, 'Rogue Smoke', -1, -1, '6', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Rogue Smoke(previously known as Welkommen on draft) is a German style Rauchbier (Smoke Beer), which was inspired by the Fall of the Berlin Wall. Most rauch brews are bottom fermented, however Rogue Smoke, is top fermented. It is orange-amber in hue with a', 0, '2010-07-22'),
