(4214, 247, 'Dark Mild', 1, 10, '4', '0', '0', 0, '', 'To quote Dr. John Harrison, a great influence on my brewing, "Mild ale is the only beer with an uninterrupted history from medieval times to the present day." The "mild" means low hop bitterness, "...which is the only essential feature of a mild ale." The', 0, '2010-07-22'),
