(4659, 459, 'Raison DEtre', 3, 29, '8', '0', '0', 0, '', 'A deep, mahogany ale brewed with beet sugar, green raisins, and Belgian-style yeast. As complex as a fine, red wine. Voted "American Beer of the Year" in January 2000 by Malt Advocate Magazine.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
