(4662, 459, 'Theobroma', -1, -1, '9', '0', '0', 0, '', 'This beer is based on chemical analysis of pottery fragments found in Honduras which revealed the earliest known alcoholic chocolate drink used by early civilizations to toast special occasions.  The discovery of this beverage pushed back the earliest use', 0, '2010-07-22'),
