(4667, 741, 'Kirin Ichiban', -1, -1, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'From Brewerys site: With his gold label and Special Premium Reserve appellation, Ichiban outclasses and outperforms.In 1990, Ichibans debut made a splash in the world of super premium beers. The luxurious single wort (or first press) process yields a', 0, '2010-07-22'),
