(4687, 1244, 'Holy Cow IPA', 3, 31, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'For hops lovers - this bitter ale is pale colored and made with a blend of 6 different malts and 5 different hops. This ale is dry-hopped for extra flavor and aroma.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
