(4804, 908, 'Sundog', 3, 33, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Sundog is an amber ale as deep as the copper glow of a Lake Michigan sunset. Its biscuit malt give Sundog a toasty character and a subtle malty sweetness. Sundog brings out the best in grilled foods, caramelized onions, nutty cheese, barbecue, or your fav', 0, '2010-07-22'),
