(4815, 853, 'Celis Grand Cru', 5, 72, '8', '0', '0', 0, '', 'A GABF Gold Medal winner for 2007, this Belgian style strong ale, bright and golden colored is brewed with a hint of orange peel and coriander. This balanced, pleasant to drink brew, will sneak up on you. Consume with caution.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
