(4838, 858, 'Envy', -1, -1, '7', '0', '0', 0, '', 'ENVY Imperial Pilsner obsessively desires to be better than the worldÃ¢â‚¬â„¢s most common lager. Envy vies for attention with its beautifully bright, golden color and tightly-formed crown. Intense yet true pilsner malt provides the perfect base for profu', 0, '2010-07-22'),
