(5018, 396, 'Coopers Cave Pale Ale', 1, 1, '0', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Coopers Cave Pale Ale is an English Pale Ale throughout.It is a full bodied light colored ale with evenly pronounced hop bitterness. The grain bill consists of two English Pale Malts and an English Crystal Malt. The brewers favorite...need we say more.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
