(5225, 1089, 'Haywords 5000', 8, 95, '8', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Launched in the year 1983, Haywards 5000 is synonymous with strong beer in India. Haywards 5000 is brewed with the choicest of malts and hops lending itself to a unique flavour profile to suit the Indian taste and preference. Haywards 5000 is the hallmark', 0, '2010-07-22'),
