(5228, 1055, 'Richbrau Oatmeal Stout', 1, 21, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'If you donÃ¢â‚¬â„¢t do dark beers, do yourself a favor and cancel that policy for this Oatmeal Stout. Keywords: Sweet Lusciousness; Roasty chocolate. Served on a nitro tap.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
