(5256, 1245, 'Hellsmoke Porter', 2, 25, '6', '0', '0', 0, '', 'A roasty robust porter. Brewed with malt that I smoke over alder and apple wood.  Goes great with steak, burgers, as well as barbecued, grilled, or smoked food. Kielbasi! Cheeses? Try it with Gouda, Brie, Swiss, or Havarti.', 0, '2010-07-22');
