(5760, 858, 'Bathtub Gin Gruit Ale', 11, 126, '8', '0', '0', 0, '', 'This gruit ale was inspired by the Phish song of the same name. A traditional gruit in style, Bathtub Gin was brewed without hops. Instead Ben spiced his beer with botanicals typically used to flavor gin: juniper berries, orris root, angelica root, grains', 0, '2010-07-22'),
