(5766, 44, 'Michelob Irish Red', 2, 22, '0', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Born of Irish tradition, this all-malt ale uses kilned and toasted malts to produce its all-natural, signature red shade. A beer with exceptional balance, Irish Red displays an initial sweetness that fades to a clean, dry finish.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
