(5790, 673, 'Gulden Fraug Belgian Ale', 5, 65, '11', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Smooth malt flavors of this golden Belgian-style abbey ale are complimented by traditional imported ingredients. A slightly spicy and complex flavor makes this European celebration-style beer unique and refreshing', 0, '2010-07-22'),
(5791, 673, 'Wild Frog Wheat', 4, 50, '6', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Traditional German-style, unfiltered wheat beer, with a lively balanced flavor. Although no fruit or spices were used in the brewing, these flavors are created by fermentation with special yeast from the oldest brewery in the world. Try Wild Frog Wheat wi', 0, '2010-07-22'),
