(5816, 718, 'Manheim Red', 3, 33, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Our flagship beer, is amber to red in color with a medium body, slight caramel sweetness, and a balance more towards malt than hops. This beer is a true crowd-pleaser and keeps you coming back for more.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
