(5834, 634, 'Harpoon Leviathan', 3, 32, '10', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Harpoon Leviathan Imperial IPA will challenge your senses and your palate. As the vibrant aroma rushes out of your glass you will notice the blend of piney and tropical fruit notes.  At first sip, this big beer starts with apowerful hop bitterness up fron', 0, '2010-07-22'),
(5835, 1044, 'Full Moon Pale Rye Ale', 11, 119, '6', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Tawny red and full of malt and hops, Full Moons unique flavor truly satisfies. The smooth sweetness of malted rye and barley is complemented by generous helpings of Willamette and Cascade hops, resulting in an assertive American amber ale.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
(5836, 1044, 'Rio Blanco Pale Ale', 3, 26, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Deep golden and malty, with a spicy hop flavor and well balanced hop bitterness, Rio Blanco is a uniquely Texan interpretation of an English-style pale ale. Czech Saaz hops provide a crisp finish and delicate aroma.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
(5837, 742, 'Hitachino Nest XH', 3, 30, '8', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Dark ale with a tan head. Subtle sake flavor from cask aging.', 0, '2010-07-22'),
