(5888, 1412, 'FA', 1, 4, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'FA is no small beer: despite its deceptively pale golden colour, it boasts a big, smooth flavour and strong punch. Brewed with the finest English malts, and conditioned in cask with dry hops to produce fresh hop aromas and a fuller flavour, delighting the', 455, '2011-05-17'),
