(5890, 1412, 'Dark Mild', 1, 11, '3', '0', '0', 0, '', 'This is a smooth, full flavoured, truly dark mild with a rich creamy head. It has a full body and distinctive roasted malt taste, balanced by its fresh hop character. Complex flavours and aromas are achieved by blending deeply roasted malt and adding a se', 455, '2011-05-17'),
(5891, 1412, '2008 Culture Beer', 1, 3, '5', '0', '0', 0, '', 'A full, clean and refreshing pale coloured bitter with an abundance of citrus hop character created by the blend of dry and late hopping techniques. It also has subtle hints of malt and fruit on aroma and palate which gives the beer a well rounded balanc', 455, '2011-05-17'),
(5892, 1413, 'Iron Rail IPA', 1, 2, '7', '0', '0', 0, '', 'English Style India Pale Ale, Maris Otter 2-row, Canadian Honey Malt and Belgian Crystal. Centennial, Kent Golding, and Cascade are added Five times during the process, including Dry Hopping. Aroma: Earthy, Citrusy, and Resinous Tasting/Flavor: Orangy an', 462, '2011-05-23'),
(5893, 1414, 'Black Creek Porter', 11, 130, '0', '0', '0', 0, '', 'Porter is a dark-coloured beer developed in the 1750s. Porter has a heavier flavour and aroma and a slightly sweet taste. Its name probably originates in the belief that this strong, nourishing drink was ideal for hard-working porters and labourers. Black', 483, '2011-06-08'),
(5894, 1416, 'Vivant Tripel', 5, 61, '9', '0', '0', 0, '', 'A classic golden ale, with subtle esters of banana and bubblegum. This beer pours with a creamy head and ends with a sweetness of light Belgian candi sugars. Our brewmaster aged this ale for an extended period to round out the flavors. A great traditional', 494, '2011-06-22'),
